-- Hitachi Zosen Raises Full-Year Net Income Forecast 13% to $111 Million
-- B y   A d a m   L e
-- 2010-11-04T06:05:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-04/hitachi-zosen-raises-full-year-net-income-forecast-13-to-111-million.html
Hitachi Zosen Corp. raised its full-
year net income forecast 13 percent to 9 billion yen ($111
million), according to a statement handed out today at the Osaka
Securities Exchange.  To contact the reporter on this story:
